CHAT.comment: At home in the late afternoon, just before BM leaves for the day. FA has prepared some food for XB to eat and tells MO about it just before he leaves. XB has just awakened from her nap and M feeds her for much of the visit. XB and her family live together with her paternal grandparents in an Academy of Sciences apartment.
Caregiving is shared between BM, FA, and MO. Part of this visit was also videotaped.
